features: Soft and Lightweight - Our bedding comforter sets is made of premium fabric which is ultra soft, hypoallergenic, breathable and sweat-absorbent. The comforter is filled with 240gsm cloud-like down alternative, which is thick enough to keep you warm but it's also fairly light weight. Even in a cold place in winter, you only need to add another blanket, and don’t need to buy a new comforter. This comforter set is perfect for all season, we want you to be comfortable all year round.

Bedding in A Bag - You'll get all the bedding you need and won't need to spend extra time looking for something else to match your bedroom. And we porvide multi colors for you to choose. The 7 pieces queen comforter set includes 1 comforter (88"x 88"), 1 flat sheet (90"x 102"), 1 fitted sheet (60"x 80"x14"), 2 pillowcase (20"x 30") and 2 pillow sham (20"x 26").

Exquisite Seersucker Design - This queen comforter set is designed with textured seersucker, slightly pleated to bring vivid and three-dimensional wave visual effect, adding a sense of romance to your bedroom and making you fall in love with this design at first sight. The hidden patchwork design ensures that the filling stays in place and prevents shifting or clumping after washing.

Easy to Care - Machine wash in the gentle cycle with cold water. Sun-dry or tumble dry on low heat. Do not bleach. Do not iron. Tips: Our comforter set is vacuum packaged, it will fluffy up nicely after airing it for a few hours or putting it into dryer on low for 15-20 mins.

No Risk Shopping - if you have any problem about our product, please feel free to contact us for an exchange or refund. Love's cabin strives to provide 1-Month return and replacement service & life-time free customer service. We want our customers to be 100% happy and satisfied!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was impressed with the quality of this blanket. It was a hit with my teenage daughter for sure

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great price for a cute set
reviews.reviewText: Got the grey queen size set and I'm super happy with it. The sheets feel like a silky cotton, the comforter fluffs out nicely after washing and drying, and I love that the texture is already wrinkly so it looks casual. I was worried about the lack of reviews and cheap price but I couldn't be happier! This feels like much better quality than cheap sets I've gotten from big chain stores.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Amazing, soft, lightweight but still heavy and warm, and the prettiest smokey blue color. I love this bedding set, and it looks gorgeous in my son's room. A very masculine color, soft sheets and gorgeous pattern. I couldn't be happier with the quality, the size, the everything. If you're considering getting this, DO IT!!!! You won't be disappointed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Absolute oh my gosh I absolutely love this bed set so awesome it's beautiful and soft.It is not too thick of a blanket but also not too thin it's perfect in the middle a wonderful layering blanket or warmer weather blanket by itself, it comes with one pillowcase and one sham, which I was a little perplexed by because I really would have preferred two pillowcases or two shams but not one of each, it looks a little lopsided LOL but that's okay! I can always match some different pillowcases to it and different shams, that really doesn't affect my rating much at all.the packaging was awesome, all vacuum sealed and clean, very impressed overall.I haven't opened it yet because I want to use it for a guest bedroom which I have not set up fully yet and I don't want to get it dirty but when I have it all busted out and washed and fluffed I will take some more pictures! I highly recommend! Also just looking at this it would be a wonderful gift ❤️Cheers

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love this bed in a bag. The look, the feel, the texture and the color. The comforter is soft, warm and breathable and the sheets feel great on my skin. The design of the set is eye catching.This bed in a bag was a great selection on my part and I hope that it will last me for years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love the seersucker texture of the comforter. You don't have to worry about wrinkles and it adds a little something different. The comforter and the sheets are incredibly soft. They are a medium shade of navy and work well in our moon themed room.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not the best material
reviews.reviewText: A very…meh… purchase. Color is ok and material is pretty much a glorified trash bag. I can’t shrink wrap it back like they had it so I guess I’m keeping it. I’m buying a new comforter and just using the sheets from this set. Also it’s definitely not oversized like in the picture. It barely even covers the side of the mattress so yeah like I said a very meh purchase. I won’t be buying from again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Quality is ok for the price im not a huge fan of the texture either but it is very simple snd matches with nearly anything. Pretty comfortable and soft to the touch.
